              <h2>Step‑by‑step: using the Michigan income tax calculator</h2>
              <ol>
                <li>
                  <strong>Select your filing status.</strong> This helps you
                  think in terms of your household income.
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Choose income type.</strong> If you know your salary,
